node.text: What a year it’s been - pandemic, Beirut explosions, George Floyd, Brianna Taylor, and so much more. If you reading this, you are one of the fortunate ones who made it. Thanks for following, for the support and encouragement. Wishing you a better year ahead, please stay safe and healthy, sending you lots of love, Tracey xxx PS - sound comes and goes, sorry, let’s blame it on 2020 🤷🏻‍♀️😂❤️

node.text: Hats off to @phillipshouse for this incredible initiative- donate $25 to a charity of your choice corresponding to the global pandemic, and they will give you a gift! node.text: ARE YOU READY FOR 163 CARATS, D FLAWLESS??? 🤭 This weeks #SundayFunday post is probably the most beautiful diamond I’ve ever seen… a detachable stone, so clean and pure and beautiful that it’s worth watching the entire video to see this stone in all its glory! node.text: SENDING LOVE AND PRAYERS TO DALLAS @dallasprincecollections , who is currently in hospital fighting COVID, pneumonia, and ensuing loss of vision in her one eye. Dallas is a true beauty, inside and out, and I had the pleasure of meeting her at @agta_gems Tucson show a few years back, where I loved her collection, especially this locket. I was instantly touched by her kindness, and her passion for gems and jewels. Please join me in wishing Dallas a full and speedy recovery. 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻❤️❤️❤️ #thediamondsgirl #dallasprincedesigns #dallasprince #agta #locket #fuckcovid19 #jewelry #gems
